  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605440/extras/23d9eee642755a3dc943d98c4613c584.avif?t=1634415986\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ragdoll Madness</h2> <strong>is a physics based game. Complete levels by solving puzzles,</strong><br><strong>Take control of your character with physics-based ragdoll mechanics! Move and Grab the objects and Complete Levels!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605440/extras/d4adba048b3de9867ec0abbc4e8f997d.poster.avif?t=1634415986\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605440/extras/d4adba048b3de9867ec0abbc4e8f997d.webm?t=1634415986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605440/extras/d4adba048b3de9867ec0abbc4e8f997d.mp4?t=1634415986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create your own levels or mods Unity Engine!</h2><strong><br>You can create Mod or Map using Unity Engine and C#!<br>It depends on your imagination, You can see how to do it in the community section!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605440/extras/31c0f1a6ad392157ec0f236afc1395ad.avif?t=1634415986\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Split Screen!</h2><strong>If you have Keyboard and Gamepad, You can play with friend Split-Screen!<br>and You can Play with Remote Play Together!</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605440/extras/e444a862fbe40afddf5c364f353bcb14.avif?t=1634415986\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard</h2><strong>WASD - Movement<br>Arrow Keys - Movement<br>Space - Jump<br>Mouse Buttons (Hold) - Grab Objects</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gamepad</h2><strong>Joystick - Movement<br>South Button - Jump<br>Left Trigger,Right Trigger - Grab Objects</strong>",
